{"id":232891227,"title":"戴佛牌的感覺","content":"小妹我配戴佛牌10幾年了\n如果忘記戴還會覺得怪怪的\n\n想到之前高中在補習班\n有一位同學對靈界的朋友有感應\n那天聚集的比較多讓他不太舒服\n但是她發現祂們都不會靠近我\n就跑來問我為什麼會這樣\n\n我其實也一頭霧水\n畢竟我什麼都感應不到\n他一問我才想到我身上戴著佛牌\n因為那天我朋友越來越不舒服\n就請求我借她戴一下我的佛牌\n\n不久之後他跟我說他好多了\n祂們真的也不會靠近她了\n\n我也半信半疑的\n不知道戴著佛牌真的可以阻隔祂們靠近嗎？\n而且佛牌換別人戴也一樣可以？\n\n不知道版上各位前輩怎麼看？https://i.imgur.com/1OZZIFY.jpg\nhttps://i.imgur.com/4yuFrtV.jpg","excerpt":"小妹我配戴佛牌10幾年了，如果忘記戴還會覺得怪怪的，想到之前高中在補習班，有一位同學對靈界的朋友有感應，那天聚集的比較多讓他不太舒服，但是她發現祂們都不會靠近我，就跑來問我為什麼會這樣，我其實也一頭霧","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"37a78696-f6a6-48ec-a19f-688f799a2aed","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-14T14:55:04.804Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-14T14:55:04.804Z","commentCount":26,"likeCount":17,"tags":[],"topics":["佛牌"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"靈異","forumAlias":"marvel","school":"國立勤益科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":17}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/1OZZIFY.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/4yuFrtV.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"fa6fbff2-da1a-4822-a633-fdcfee8f2343","url":"https://i.imgur.com/1OZZIFYl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/1OZZIFYl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/1OZZIFYl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-14T14:55:04.804Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-14T14:55:04.804Z"},{"id":"fa6fbff2-da1a-4822-a633-fdcfee8f2343","url":"https://i.imgur.com/1OZZIFY.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/1OZZIFY","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/1OZZIFYl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-14T14:55:04.804Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-14T14:55:04.804Z"},{"id":"2ef1fd35-cd9c-4c56-aa0b-f66c9e999161","url":"https://i.imgur.com/4yuFrtV.jpg","n